Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.95,0:00:09.27,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:12.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:16.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:24.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.22,0:00:34.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:41.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.95,0:00:48.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.91,0:00:56.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:59.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:03.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.43,0:01:07.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.43,0:01:10.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:14.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:18.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.15,0:01:21.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.15,0:01:25.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.66,0:01:29.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.37,0:01:32.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:35.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.67,0:01:41.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:49.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally found some...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people with such nice memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.75,0:04:29.75,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Was It Lost? Stolen? Who Are You?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can still eat lots more...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And who are these people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey.\N--Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know anything about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--I'm Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a cook at the Sea Restaurant Baratie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.82,0:05:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember going to sleep in\Nmy room yesterday like always,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but then I woke up in this strange\Nplace with you complete strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.59,0:05:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you guys didn't save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left Fusha Village and went sailing,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.43,0:06:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but then I ran into this gigantic whirlpool...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.14,0:06:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember getting into a\Nbarrel and getting all dizzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and then I suddenly wound up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you guys had saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.86,0:06:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.11,0:06:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember having a silly conversation\Nwith Kaya-chan yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then playing with Pepper and\Nthe gang before hitting the hay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't remember a thing after that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And these guys are the same?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, do you know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea why we're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.01,0:06:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going on,\Nmuch less who these guys are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to bluff for now...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.31,0:06:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no surprise you've forgotten\Neverything up until yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.15,0:06:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you were attacked\Nby a legendary giant whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.65,0:06:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A legendary giant whale?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:07:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I defeated it and saved\Nyou guys after it swallowed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Really?! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you asked!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Usopp, leader of a great pirate crew\Nthat rules the seas of the East Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the people's undying praise!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Captain Usopp" is what they call me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Captain Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You know him?\N--No, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Better watch what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Usopp Pirates have 8,000 members--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.61,0:07:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! 8,000?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, you're both my\Nsubordinates as of yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.37,0:07:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Eep! You could tell?!\N--See, you even admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I admitted it! You dirty schemer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a funny guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Don't make fun of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a proud man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.76,0:08:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have so much pride that people\Ncall me "Usopp the Proud"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.94,0:08:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just... I feel like I've done this before...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.95,0:08:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just leave it at that for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What we need is food. People\Ncan't think on empty stomachs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Food?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, didn't you say you're a cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A first-class cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.59,0:08:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is a ship, there's gotta be something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cook...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who are you, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? I'm the man who's\Ngonna be King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.82,0:09:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa. This ship's been through a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! An island!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have bad news, guys. Our navigator is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Who the heck are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they also your subordinates, Captain Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?! Y-Yeah, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys lost your memories, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I finally understand how a foolish\Nmoth feels as it flies into a lamp...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People can't help but leap into\Nthe brilliant radiance of others!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, pretty ladies! Your names, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're free, what do you\Nsay to dinner tonight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this guy's funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He suddenly has a different personality...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,0:09:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh, who are these guys?! And where am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:10:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that... backwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What the heck is that?\N--It's a deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.85,0:10:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, human! I'm a reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let's catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop! It's creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.74,0:10:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, girl! Help me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.82,0:10:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! S-Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.62,0:10:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy... Where do I even begin to explain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Listen, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're currently located in...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said we're in the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten that too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.26,0:11:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you so happy for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say the Grand Line is\Nteeming with monsters and stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be freaked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, it doesn't seem so\Ndifferent from the regular sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.27,0:11:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really the Grand Line?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.44,0:11:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navigator?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who, me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you recognize what's on your arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.28,0:11:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Log Pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses don't work here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:12:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so islands' magnetic fields\Nare used for navigation instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what that tool is for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's essential for crossing the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Miss. I need to return\Nto my restaurant in the East Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.05,0:12:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I go about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.77,0:12:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't recommend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.64,0:12:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been traveling a long time;\Nheading back alone would be suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've continually followed\Nthe Log Pose's directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's led us to this coral-surrounded isle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all too much at once for me to believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I be cheerfully\Ntraveling with people like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.59,0:12:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man! That's a pirate flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! It's a pirate ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's right! It's the great\NCaptain Usopp's pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:12:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.68,0:13:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, Captain Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it me, or is that skull wearing a straw hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That just means... this hat is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch my straw hat! I'll kick\Nyour butt if you do that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.45,0:13:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I thought you lost your memory?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember this! It's my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treasure...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.96,0:13:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a precious treasure a friend\Ngave me when I was little!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swore on this hat I'd become\Na pirate and gather a crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates this, pirates that! What a stupid era!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at least now I know that\Neverything you've said is nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate pirates! What I like\Nare money and tangerines!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.41,0:14:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that I'd\Nbe traveling with pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now. Might wanna watch your tone, girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.42,0:14:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tangerines? Like those?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.09,0:14:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tangerine trees...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.85,0:14:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.02,0:14:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...! It just grew an arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystery tangerines?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.23,0:14:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.48,0:14:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More important is that tangerine...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is one of Bellemere-san's tangerines!\NI know that much for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are her tangerines doing on this ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I don't know\Nmuch about that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you check the\Nship's logbook in your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.75,0:14:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I recall, there's a picture\Nof your Bellemere-san in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.19,0:15:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my handwriting...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at how many I got!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.68,0:15:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some of them are still green!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know better, Nami!\NYou have to pay attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? But they were nice and sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ate some?! They're\Nmerchandise, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. We can eat these ones ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.69,0:15:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! You're a big meanie, Nojiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, get to work, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something might've happened\Nto Cocoyashi Village...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... what exactly is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neato reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reindeer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.36,0:16:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great when thinly sliced,\Nslowly simmered with vegetables,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.07,0:16:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and made into a stew...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! We can eat it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reindeer steak with berry sauce is also superb.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Steak, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:17:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't no food!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't eat him. He's the ship's doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He's a brilliant doctor\Nbeyond even human compare.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.69,0:17:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being praised by humans doesn't\Nmake me happy at all, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.20,0:17:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you sure seem happy to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a reindeer who ate the Human Human\NFruit and gained human abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, I ate the Flower Flower Fruit\Nand gained Devil Fruit powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Luffy has eaten a Devil Fruit as well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.96,0:17:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I ate the Gum Gum Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm made of rubber!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.93,0:17:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Three people with Devil Fruit powers...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.18,0:17:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys pirates?! Real pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.06,0:17:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. You are too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:18:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! As of today, you're a\Nmember of the Usopp Pirates too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.82,0:18:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! How come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're taking him seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.78,0:18:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, along with one other person,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.03,0:18:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we've been crossing these seas\Nas a seven-member pirate crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One other person?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.54,0:18:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come down, Swordsman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys're making quite a\Nracket so early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.13,0:18:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're interrupting my morning nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who are you?! State your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to give your name\Nfirst when asking someone's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.60,0:18:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh...\N--I'm Luffy! Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.19,0:18:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Roronoa Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As in "Pirate Hunter"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.73,0:18:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never once gone by that name.\NI just wound up with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.32,0:18:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still a bounty hunter, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only did it when I needed money to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.00,0:18:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.91,0:18:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I take it you're only here 'cause\Nyou were targeting a pirate ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me. I got no idea why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys notorious pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.22,0:19:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're out to get us after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.39,0:19:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fine, bring it on! I have 8,000\Npeople under my command!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.89,0:19:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Then I bet you're worth a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I needed some food money anyway.\NI'll be more than happy to take you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.57,0:19:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! That's not what I meant! C-C-Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have a bounty.\NNot even a single Berry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get out of here somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.55,0:19:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.22,0:20:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is enough to buy Cocoyashi Village\Nback and have money left over!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now how do I haul it out...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.59,0:20:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.69,0:20:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.04,0:21:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! It can run on the water too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? She left!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.96,0:21:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing's so neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.05,0:21:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no idea what's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems like there's\Nno point in me staying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.52,0:21:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? He left too. What's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.11,0:21:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck's going on around here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't the slightest, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.25,0:21:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a real conundrum...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.98,0:22:09.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A piece of a dream that we started grasping
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:12.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing after something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:18.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We send our aspirations sailing into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:20.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we're exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:23.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a compass that can\Nsearch for something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:29.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think we can keep it forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.13,0:22:32.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the dream\Nthat we will reach someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:35.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to be adults as we\Nare now as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.05,0:22:37.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We pray to this endless sky that we look up at
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.80,0:22:40.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.89,0:22:43.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild fantasies from our childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:46.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We trace unforgettable memories
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.52,0:22:52.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And try to keep the embers\Nburning that still consume us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.19,0:22:55.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To this familiar sunny sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.07,0:22:57.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Together we entrust our feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:23:00.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We go beyond the changing time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.41,0:23:08.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.25,0:23:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is crazy! I'd never team up with pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.76,0:23:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is my handwriting in the logbook...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.43,0:23:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and the treasure's mine too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.43,0:23:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Whoa! What kind of scene is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.27,0:23:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Hey! Was it you?!\NGive our memories back!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.60,0:23:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Mysterious Boy with a Horn\Nand Robin's Deduction!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.48,0:23:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're never gonna be King of the Pirates!!
